  "title": "Supply & Production Coordinator - WCAN",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Develop and manage production schedules to meet targets and fulfill customer orders.</li>\n  <li>Analyze production data and make schedule adjustments to optimize resource utilization.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with the sales team to align production plans with customer demand.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with procurement to ensure timely availability of raw materials and components.</li>\n  <li>Monitor inventory levels and adjust production accordingly to maintain optimal stock levels.</li>\n  <li>Work closely with quality control to ensure production meets required standards and customer specifications.</li>\n  <li>Identify and implement opportunities for process improvement in production workflows.</li>\n  <li>Prepare and present reports on production schedules, inventory status, and key performance metrics for management.</li>\n  <li>Proficient in Microsoft Office and other relevant software, with strong data analysis capabilities.</li>\n  <li>Partner with the production team to resolve process issues and minimize delays or quality concerns.</li>\n  <li>Liaise with freight forwarders and customers to coordinate delivery schedules and logistics arrangements.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>2–3 years of experience in supply planning or similar roles within manufacturing companies</li>\n  <li>Holds a Diploma in Inventory Management or a related discipline</li>\n  <li>Acquired hands-on skills through on-the-job training within the company</li>\n  <li>Strong coordination and organizational skills with attention to detail</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication abilities for effective interaction with both customers and internal teams</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p>EA Personnel: Nyon Hock Sen (Aden)</p>\n<p>EA Personnel Reg No: R24124070</p>",
